-Warriors!

18
00:01:46,372 --> 00:01:48,608
I want to see blood out
on that field tonight.

19
00:01:48,608 --> 00:01:50,310
[all]
Yes, sir!

20
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,377
My boy is going to lead you

21
00:01:51,377 --> 00:01:52,645
to victory out there tonight.

22
