but not you.

277
00:17:43,695 --> 00:17:45,664
Mac.

278
00:17:45,664 --> 00:17:49,134
Let's just leave.

279
00:17:49,134 --> 00:17:50,436
Tonight.

280
00:17:50,436 --> 00:17:54,673
