-Okay.

297
00:18:39,418 --> 00:18:40,886
Now let's celebrate.

298
00:18:40,886 --> 00:18:42,387
-You want a plate?
-No.

299
00:18:42,387 --> 00:18:43,856
This is good.

300
00:18:47,292 --> 00:18:48,727
[Duncan]
Mac Attack!

301
00:18:51,763 --> 00:18:53,398
I got pie and game tape.

302
00:18:56,301 --> 00:18:57,836
