492
00:34:07,645 --> 00:34:09,714
[instrumental music]

493
00:34:15,319 --> 00:34:16,721
Come on.

494
00:34:19,090 --> 00:34:22,427
Same make, same model,
same everything.

495
00:34:26,697 --> 00:34:28,266
[chuckles]

496
00:34:32,336 --> 00:34:34,405
-I love you.
