for you.

499
00:34:57,695 --> 00:34:59,297
[Mac]
Are you sure?

500
00:35:22,253 --> 00:35:23,454
Wait, stop, stop.

501
00:35:23,454 --> 00:35:24,856
I would die for you.

502
00:35:24,856 --> 00:35:26,624
Stop. Stop, stop.

503
00:35:26,624 --> 00:35:28,726
