-Hi.

509
00:35:51,349 --> 00:35:52,583
Come on in.

510
00:35:52,583 --> 00:35:53,851
I brought you
a little something.

511
00:35:53,851 --> 00:35:56,254
-Oh, thank you.
-Oh, thank you so much.

512
00:35:56,254 --> 00:35:57,855
I figured we could all spend
some time together.

513
00:35:57,855 --> 00:36:00,424
Of course.

514
00:36:00,424 --> 00:36:03,194
